name: Lavender Fields
description: Deep Lavender Faceted Amethyst Bead paired with Hand Hammered Vermeil Discs on 14 Kt GF Ear Wires.

name: Seaside
description: Casual and dainty, perfect for a Seaside Wedding. Luminous Salt Water Pearl paired with Hand Hammered Discs on 14 Kt Ear Wires.

name: Cherry Cordial
description: Sweet and Sexy...these earrings are simple and great for the office or a night out. Cherry colored Rubies and Hand Hammer Vermeil Discs. Just enough dangle! The Disc are about the size of a nickle. On a 14 kt GF earwire.

name: Purple Rain
description: These luscious earrings will have you singing with joy. Large Faceted Amethyst Drop surrounded in a Vermeil Bezel accented by smaller 4mm Faceted Amethyst beads all dangle from a Ornate Vermeil Chandelier Finding. They measure 2 1/4 inches long x 1 1/4 wide.

name: Three's Company
description: This lovely trio is sure to make you smile. Faceted Ruby Drops, Faceted Carnelian and Deep Purple Amethyst compliment each other. All dangle from a twisted 14 kt decorative jumpring.

name: Follow the Yellow Brick Road
description: Magical and elegance in the simplest form. 8mm Salt Water Pearl, Vermeil and Delicate Green Faceted Emerald Rondelle combined to create understated beauty.

name: Running Deer
description: While photographing this piece in the woods near my house 3 deer ran across the path in front of me...hence the name. This double strand necklace has an earthy native American feel. Made of natural American turquoise, red coral, shell heishi beads, Deer Antler Pendant accented with a Turquoise Cab. Finished with a Sterling Silver S clasp.

name: Red Carpet
description: The name says it all. These earrings were made to wear on the red carpet. Large and elegant. Ornate Vermeil Filigree with a huge set Ruby accented by two smaller Faceted Drop Rubies will get the Oohs and Ahhs at any event!

name: The Color Purple
description: Deep Purple 6mm Faceted Amethyst beads accented with Sterling Silver Daisy Spacers and Bead Caps. Made with Sterling Silver Rolo Chain and Special Slide Bead that can be adjusted to fit.

name: Red, Red Wine
description: Beautiful 6mm Faceted Wine Colored Garnets accented with Sterling Silver Daisy spacers and Tiny Bead Caps. Bracelet is strung on  beading wire and made adjustable with a special slide bead.

name: Blood of Venus
description: This petite bracelet of Italian Red Coral and Sterling Silver is a classic. Wear alone or with other bracelets make this stylish piece a must have. Sterling Silver Indian Daisy Spacers and 1mm Rolo Chain with a special slide bead make this bracelet adjustable.

name: Chain Reaction
description: Hammered 14 Kt GF Chain Links accented with Faceted Verticle Drilled Ruby Drops, Faceted Amethyst Rondelles and Faceted Ruby Rondelles and Vermeil Daisy Spacers.

name: From Russia With Love
description: Beautiful Green Natural Chrome Diopside Faceted Drops from Russia, accented by 2 1/2 mm White Fresh Water Pearls hanging from Sterling Silver Chain.

name: Kiss of the Dragon Lady
description: 10mm Tiger Eye and Black Onyx Beads accented with Vermeil Daisy Spacers and Melon Beads. Showcasing a Beautiful Hand Carved Black Onyx Bead with Dragon Motif Gilted with 22 Kt Gold. Strung on durable Stretchy Cord. Size 71/2 inches. Students Tiger Eye is a good companion in test taking and important meetings.

name: Geisha
description: The Japanese symbol of Power and Authority...is accented with Deep Red Chinese Crystals, Enameled Bead Caps and Chinese Enameled Swans. The Golden Chains trail to the shoulders.

name: Golden Dragon
description: Looking for a piece for that special guy in your life? Look no further. This bracelet is made of a carved Tiger Eye bead that is gilted with 22 Kt Gold, Black Onyx, 10 mm Tiger Eye and Vermeil Melon Beads & Daisy spacers. Strung on strong stretchy cord for ease of wear. It is 8 inches around.

name: Circle Of Life
description:
This is a statement necklace with a little secret...Beautiful Carved Red Coral Melon Beads Accented with Indian Silver Bead Caps and Beads. The Large Filigree Pendant is an Antique Indian Silver Bracelet that can be removed from the necklace and be worn alone. 
Versatile and bold.

name: 5th Avenue
description: Vermeil and Flattened Faceted Barrel Shaped Smokey Quartz Beads.Interchanged with Faceted Smokey Quartz Rondelles and 8mm Vermeil Melon Beads, ending with Heavy Vermeil Toggle. Comes with Matching Earrings. Necklace is 181/2 inches Long.

name: Empress of Cathay
description: Fit for Royalty. These Beautiful Light Green Carved Burmese Jade Links make a impressive companion to the Lusterous Deep Green Faceted Fresh Water Pearl, accented by a Indian Silver Bead Cap.

name: Three's a Charm
description: Everyone can use a little extra Luck & Protection, right? Well this necklace is for you. The first charm is a small Carved Bone Elephant from India, second is a Turkish Eye of God Bead and last but not least is a Traditional Charm from the Caribbean...made of Red Coral & Jet(Azabache). Worn to protect from The Evil Eye. The Trio is on a Sterling Silver "W" Clasp that is also a Pendant holder. The Sterling Silver Rolo chain is 24 inches long.

name: Glitterati
description: Silver and Gold has never been so Glamourous. These Shoulder Sweepers Shimmer and Shine, made of Swarovski Crystals, Gold Plated Czech Glass Drops and Seed Beads. #earrings #Shoulder Sweepers

name: Taj Mahal
description: Carved Purple Amethyst Beads End in Hand Carved Twist Drops. Accented with Decorative Vermeil Head Pins and Small Vermeil Rondelles on Gold Filled Wire and Ball End Ear Wires. Elegant and One of a Kind Just like the Taj Mahal.

name: Dark Lady
description: Dark and mysterious, describes these glittering shouder sweepers. Made with Swarovski Crystals and size 15 Seed Beads accented with Bali Silver Links and Sterling Silver Earwires. Strung On Nylon Thread for strength and a nice swing. These are sure to keep The Dark Lady Dancing! Oh did I say these measure 6 inches long...

name: Florecitas
description: This dainty necklace is delicate yet striking. Blush Pink Carved Coral flowers, White Freshwater Pearls and 14 kt Gold Filled beads with simple Gold Filled Fish Hook clasp. The necklace is about 17 1/2 inches long.

name: Double Dragon
description: Milky Green New Jade, Peridot,Faceted Light Green Phrenite, Carved New Jade Dragons and Carved New Jade Pendant with Sterling Silver Clasp. Approximately 23 inches Long

name: The Girl from Ipanema
description: This necklace screams exotic...Mother of Pearl sticks, Champagne Fresh Water Pearls and Large Tiger Cowrie Shell Pendant with Sterling Silver Hook & Eye Clasp. Make a statement wearing this one!

name: The Good Earth
description: Warm double strand earth tone Multicolored Serpentine beads with Pendant. Can be worn twisted or loose. Sterling silver clasp. 18 1/2 inches long.

name: Eye of God
description: These charms have been used by many cultures all over the world to protect against "The Evil Eye" or Malochia. These charms are made of blue glass eye beads and Sterling Silver Head Pins and Silver decorative soldered Jump Rings.

name: Rose of Siam
description: Lush Golden Vermeil Rose Ear Wires with Salt Water Pearl and Faceted Ruby Rondelle.

name: Kyoto
description: Big, Bold and Dramatic...describe these Earrings made of Vintage Japanese Cotton Pearls,Swarovski Crystals, Rondelles and Sterling Silver Filigree Earring Posts & Bead Caps.

name: Gypsy Wedding
description: Colorful Czech Glass beads, Swarovski Rondelles steal the show on Gold Plated Chandelier Finding, accented with Gold Plated Bead Caps on Vermeil Ear Wires.

name: Faerie Glamour
description: Moon Beams and Faerie Dust are captured in these magical earrings. Made of dainty Vintage Lucite Flowers, Swarovski Crystals and Sterling Silver.

name: Peruvian Dream
description: Watery Peruvian Opal Drops with Bali Silver Link.

name: Thieves in the Temple
description:
Dark Garnet Beads add mystery to these Petite Chandelier Earrings.
At one time wearing Garnets were thought to protect the wearer from thieves.

name: Sky Drop
description: Beautiful Sky Blue Faceted Drops set in Vermeil Bezel.

name: True Blue
description: Dainty Blue Kyanite paired with White Salt Water Pearls Accented with Sterling Silver Daisy Spacer on Sterling Silver Ear Wire.

name: Purple Passion
description: Rich Faceted Purple Amethyst Drop set in Vermeil Bezel. 20 x 15mm Drop

name: Turkish Delight
description: Sky Blue Turqouise Rectangle set in Vermeil Bezel accented with a White Salt Water Pearl,on Vermeil Ear Wire.

name: Sunset in Paradise
description: Fiery Orange Carnelian Drop set in Vermeil Bezel. About 20 x 15mm Drop

name: Jaded
description: Simple with a twist...beautiful carved Burma Jade accented with Salt Water Pearl and Sterling Silver beadcap.

name: Jungle Love
description: Exotic and not for the faint of heart...these beautiful earrings are sure to be a crowd pleasure. Make of Tusk Shell and Hilltribe Silver Cowrie Shell. For the lady that wants something unique and one of a kind. Tusk Shell or Dentellium are used in Native American jewelry and clothing as a status symbol and sign of weatlh.

name: Courtesan
description: These fun and funky Earrings will get attention. A Golden Fan with a Phoenix Motif is a symbol of Immortality and Uniqueness.Along with Chinese Crystal, a little Chinese Enameled Duck and  Trailing Gold Filled Chains make these Earrings a Bold Statement!!!

name: Pearls of Yemaya
description: Simple, classic and elegant. 8mm Salt Water Pearls with a Sterling Silver Beadcap and Ear Wires.Beautiful Luster!

name: Pearls of Wisdom
description: Beautiful Large Peacock Freshwater Pearls, Hand knotted on lt gray silk. Accented by a beautiful Sterling Silver box clasp with a faceted Amethyst stone. Pearls are 10mm and the length is 20 inches long.

name: Dos Aquas
description: This bracelet is made of Yellow and Blue Striped African Trade beads and Sterling Silver Beads on Black Waxed Cotton Cord.

name: Smoke Gets in Your Eyes
description: Large Faceted Smokey Quartz with three strands of Citrine and Garnet. Accented with a beautiful Sterling Silver clasp set with a Faceted Citrine Stone. 18 inches long.

name: Fields of Green
description: Lush Greens dangle from Sterling Silver Ring. Chinese Jade,Green Tourmaline, Green Faceted FWP,Peridot and New Jade make up this design.

name: Funky Buddhas
description: These lovely earrings are shoulder sweepers. Made of Turquoise, Red Coral & Carved Seeds. The seeds are carved into the image of little Buddhas! The long Sterling Silver Chain is about 61/2 inches long.

name: Bolly Wood
description: Hot Pink Dyed Chalcedony Drop with Bright Orange Faceted Carnelian Round Bead on 14 Kt Chain & Ball End Earwires.

name: Sea of India
description: Beautiful red ruby drops and white keishi freshwater pearls on 14 kt GF earwires.
